OL,3,CMan who shook his partner's toddler to
OL,4,Cdeath jailed for life
OL,6,FA man who shook his partner's toddler
OL,7,Fto death, in their Darlington home,
OL,8,Fhas been jailed for life.
OL,10,FChristopher Stockton, 38, was in sole
OL,11,Fcharge of 22-month-old Charlie Roberts
OL,12,Fwhen he suffered an unsurvivable head
OL,13,Finjury. Charlie's mother Paula
OL,14,Fadmitted neglecting him prior to the
OL,15,Fmurder.
OL,17,FRoberts, 41, was suspicious enough
OL,18,Fabout Stockton that she set up a spy
OL,19,Fcamera above her son's cot, a trial at
OL,20,FTeesside Crown Court heard in December.
