OL,3,CMan who shook his partner's toddler to
OL,4,Cdeath jailed for life
OL,6,FBut she stayed in a relationship with
OL,7,Fhim, even after she voiced her
OL,8,Fconcerns about Stockton to her brother.
OL,10,FHaving initially denied a child
OL,11,Fcruelty charge, Roberts was to
OL,12,Feventually admit neglecting her son by
OL,13,Ffailing to get Charlie medical
OL,14,Ftreatment for bruising caused by
OL,15,FStockton over several weeks.
OL,17,FHer boyfriend was convicted of murder
OL,18,Fand child cruelty.
