OL,3,CMan who shook his partner's toddler to
OL,4,Cdeath jailed for life
OL,6,FStockton was jailed at Teesside Crown
OL,7,FCourt today, for life with a minimum
OL,8,Fterm of 25 years.
OL,10,FRoberts has also been jailed for four
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FStockton, who had moved in with
OL,14,FRoberts and her little boy just seven
OL,15,Fdays earlier, was in sole charge of
OL,16,FCharlie when he inflicted a severe
OL,17,Fhead injury which caused widespread
OL,18,Fbleeding on the brain in January 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/12
