OL,6,FNicholas Lumley KC, prosecuting, told
OL,7,Fjurors that Stockton "shook or threw
OL,8,Fhim with such violence, deliberately
OL,9,Fand forcefully harming little Charlie".
OL,11,FRoberts had left the home minutes
OL,12,Fbefore to go for an eye test, and
OL,13,FStockton, who was off work ill and who
OL,14,Fhad stayed up into the early hours
OL,15,Fplaying Xbox games, must have snapped
OL,16,Fthat January morning, the court was
OL,17,Ftold.
