OL,6,FStockton rang 999 and could be heard
OL,7,Fon a recording repeatedly saying "come
OL,8,Fon mate" and "wakey wakey" to the
OL,9,Flittle boy, who was not breathing.
OL,11,FStockton was to tell paramedics,
OL,12,Fdoctors and the police that Charlie
OL,13,Fhad choked on a biscuit and that he
OL,14,Fpatted the child on the back and stuck
OL,15,Fhis fingers down the toddler's throat.
OL,17,FThe toddler died in hospital the next
OL,18,Fday.
