OL,6,FJamie Hill KC, defending Stockton,
OL,7,Ftold the court on Friday that he had
OL,8,Fno previous convictions, the murder
OL,9,Fwas not premeditated and there was no
OL,10,Fintention to kill.
OL,12,FRichard Herrmann, defending Roberts,
OL,13,Fsaid she had struggled with mental
OL,14,Fhealth issues.
OL,16,FShe wept as Mr Herrmann said: "She has
OL,17,Fto live with the knowledge that had
OL,18,Fshe acted differently it would not
OL,19,Fhave happened."
