OL,6,FNicholas Lumley KC, prosecuting, said
OL,7,FCharlie's father and two grandfathers
OL,8,Fhad written statements for the court
OL,9,Fabout their sense of loss, but all
OL,10,Fthree did not want them read out in
OL,11,Fpublic.
OL,13,FAfter Stockton's conviction, Charlie's
OL,14,Fdad Barry Greenwell said: "Charlie was
OL,15,Fa much-loved son and grandson who has
OL,16,Fbeen taken away needlessly, and has
OL,17,Fleft the whole family with a void that
OL,18,Fwill never be filled.
