OL,6,F"As a family we are processing the
OL,7,Frecent events and are trying to come
OL,8,Fto terms with the verdict and
OL,9,Finformation given that has been deeply
OL,10,Fdisturbing to ourselves."
OL,12,FDetective Superintendent Chris Barker,
OL,13,Fwho led the inquiry, said: "To install
OL,14,Fa spy camera, as Paula Roberts did,
OL,15,Fmeans there must have been concerns
OL,16,Fabout him.
OL,18,F"If you have concerns about those
OL,19,Fcaring for your children, you must
OL,20,Fact, speak out or ask for help.
