OL,6,F"Charlie had everything to live for,
OL,7,Fbut his life was cruelly cut short."
OL,9,FSentencing Stockton in court today, Mr
OL,10,FJustice Goss said the extent of
OL,11,FCharlie's internal bleeding was that
OL,12,Ftypically "found in cases of very
OL,13,Fsevere trauma such as fatal motor
OL,14,Fvehicle collisions, head crash
OL,15,Finjuries or high level multi story
OL,16,Ffalls on to concrete. "
