OL,6,FHe added: "Not only have you deprived
OL,7,Fa young child, who was resilient and
OL,8,Fexuberant, of his life, you have
OL,9,Frobbed his family of the joy of
OL,10,Fbringing up a child.
OL,12,F"No court can undo the harm you have
OL,13,Fcaused.
OL,15,F"You must have appreciated that the
OL,16,Fvery severe degree of force that you
OL,17,Ftook upon such a small child would
OL,18,Fhave inevitably have caused the most
OL,19,Fgrave injuries, if not death."
