OL,6,FDominic Tate of the Crown Prosecution
OL,7,FService said: "It is clear from the
OL,8,Fevidence in this case that Christopher
OL,9,FStockton's relationship with Charlie
OL,10,FRoberts was punctuated by incidents of
OL,11,Fviolence.
OL,13,F"After Stockton began a relationship
OL,14,Fwith Paula Roberts, Charlie sustained
OL,15,Fa series of unexplained injuries,
OL,16,Fculminating in his tragic death in
OL,17,FJanuary of last year.
