OL,6,F"Stockton had initially claimed that
OL,7,FCharlie had died after choking on
OL,8,Fsomething that morning, but we worked
OL,9,Falongside our police partners to show
OL,10,Fhow, while in Stockton's sole care, he
OL,11,Fwas tragically subjected to sufficient
OL,12,Fviolence to cause catastrophic head
OL,13,Finjuries.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts remain with the father
OL,16,Fof Charlie Roberts, for who this must
OL,17,Fremain a particularly difficult time.
OL,18,FWe sincerely hope that he can take
OL,19,Fsome measure of comfort from seeing
OL,20,Fhis son's killer jailed today."
